            "en":"Gear Ratio vs Teeth Ratio"
         },
         "description":{
            "en":"While Teeth Ratio expresses the relationship between the driver gear and the driven gear based on the number of teeth they have, Gear Ratio expresses the ratio generated by the rotations of the driver gear to the rotations of the driven gear."
         },
         "challengeType":"horizontal"
      },
